			<h2>Correspondence</h2>
			<a class="xsmall link-alt" href="https://www.thesunmagazine.org/letter-to-the-editor">Write a Letter to the Editor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>
		</div>

		<div id="article-correspondences" class="correspondences correspondences-collapsed">
								<div class="block-correspondence" id="3236">
		<blockquote class="quote-2">
			<p>Thank you for being brave enough to talk about the ambiguities of abortion [&ldquo;<a href="/article/1179">When the Bough Breaks</a>,&rdquo; Issue 198]. Your thoughtful and honest commentary strikes a rare chord that is usually drowned out by the shouts of both sides.</p>
							<p class="quote-2-author">Mary Julia Street<br>Ambler, Pennsylvania</p>
					</blockquote>
	</div>

					</div>

			</div>
    
